c: 42
v: 5
t: "tkad alsamawat ytshqqaqna, kl wahidat fawq alty tlyha; min ezmt alrhmn wjlalh tabarak wteala, walmalayikat yusabihun bihamd rbhm, wynzhwnh eamaa la ylyq bh, wayus'alun rabihim almaghfirat ldhnwb man fi al'ard min 'ahl al'iiman bh. 'ala 'iina allah hu alghafur ldhnwb mwmny ebadh, alrahim bhm"